-- pd.package: FTD tiro-font package
name: fastn-community.github.io/tiro-font

This FTD font `tiro-font` package is for your ftd web projects. To Use this
tiro-font inside `FTD` project follow below instructions.

-- ds.h3: How to use tiro-font?

-- ds.code: Add this to your FASTN.ftd
